        "Name of your project": "SCOAI OneVoice: A Secure Edge AI Translation System",
        "Briefly describe your proposed solution": "The solution is an offline Vietnamese-Chinese speech-to-speech translation system designed for edge devices. It consists of two main components: a real-time translation loop for live conversations and a post-meeting intelligence loop that automatically generates meeting minutes and contract drafts entirely offline.",
        "What makes your solution innovative or different from exi...": "Unlike standard translator apps, it provides a comprehensive, offline bilingual meeting workflow designed for privacy.  \n\nIt features a built-in \"uncertainty reviewer\" that flags low-confidence translations or ASR errors for human verification, significantly reducing risks in business contexts.  \n\nIt utilizes Small Language Models (SLMs) strictly for bounded post-meeting tasks (like term extraction and template filling) rather than real-time translation, avoiding hallucinations in legal or business agreements.",
        "Describe your technical approach": "The system uses a low-latency \"cascade\" pipeline: VAD -> ASR -> MT -> TTS.  \n\nFor speech processing, it utilizes Sherpa-ONNX running locally with Zipformer/PhoWhisper for Vietnamese and Paraformer for Chinese.  \n\nMachine translation is handled by an INT8 quantized version of the NLLB-200 600M model optimized via CTranslate2 to run on mobile CPUs/ARM64.  \n\nSpeech synthesis is powered by Piper or MeloTTS for local, natural-sounding output.  \n\nPost-meeting tasks (diarization and structured document generation) are processed using an SLM like Phi-3-mini or SmolLM2.  \n\nLatency is strictly controlled via phrase caching for emergency commands and executing INT8 quantization via NNAPI/QNN on Android edge devices.",
        "Expected language pair to support": "VN–CN",
        "Project's current development phase": "Prototype",
        "Real-world use case or industry your solution be applied": "Logistics",
        "What impact do you expect your solution to create?": "It will establish a secure, zero-cloud communication bridge for confidential business negotiations.  \n\nIt will drastically reduce administrative overhead by automating the drafting of bilingual meeting minutes and commercial contracts.  \n\nIn factory and logistics settings, ultra-low latency cached translations of emergency commands (e.g., \"Danger\", \"Stop\") will improve workplace safety.",
