        "What impact do you expect your solution to create?": "OpenVoice aims to reduce communication barriers between workers from different linguistic backgrounds, improving workplace safety, operational efficiency, and knowledge transfer.\n\nBy enabling instant multilingual communication without requiring years of language training, the solution can help workers access more employment opportunities while helping organizations build more inclusive and productive work environments.\n\nIn the long term, the technology can be expanded to support additional languages and industries, making communication more accessible for millions of workers worldwide.",
