        "Name of your project": "VoiceBridge",
        "Briefly describe your proposed solution": "We propose an on-device, ultra-low latency Speech-to-Speech translation system designed for portable Edge AI devices. The solution enables seamless, bidirectional English-Vietnamese communication in real-time without cloud dependency. By integrating optimized Streaming Automatic Speech Recognition (ASR), an efficient Neural Machine Translation (NMT) core, and Personalized Text-to-Speech (TTS) with voice-cloning capabilities, the system delivers natural conversations while preserving the original speaker's vocal characteristics and emotional tone, fully operational in offline and noisy environments.",
