        "Name of your project": "Speks",
        "Briefly describe your proposed solution": "We will build an edge AI wearable translation solution for frontline workers. The system will use a wearable microphone / bone-conduction audio device connected to a Qualcomm Android device to provide low-latency Vietnamese–English speech translation directly on-device, even in noisy industrial environments.",
        "What makes your solution innovative or different from exi...": "Most translation tools depend on cloud processing, phones held in hand, or quiet environments. Our solution is designed as a hands-free wearable system for real work environments such as factories and manufacturing sites. By combining wearable audio hardware, edge AI models, noise reduction, and low-latency speech translation, users can speak and listen naturally without stopping their work or relying fully on internet connectivity.",
        "Describe your technical approach": "Our solution will use a wearable input-output setup combined with an edge AI pipeline running on a Qualcomm Android device.\n\nThe technical flow will be:\n\nAudio capture through an off-the-shelf microphone or bone-conduction glasses/headset.\nNoise suppression and voice isolation to handle factory noise, machinery sounds, and multiple speakers.\nOn-device speech recognition to convert Vietnamese or English speech into text with low latency.\nMachine translation between Vietnamese and English.\nText-to-speech output through bone-conduction or ear audio so the user can hear the translated response hands-free.\nEdge optimization using quantized models, streaming inference, and Qualcomm NPU/DSP acceleration where possible.\n\nFor the first prototype, we will prioritize low latency, clear speech capture, offline/limited-connectivity usage, and a simple wearable user experience. The system can later be improved with custom vocabulary for manufacturing terms, speaker identification, and integration with enterprise workflows.",
        "Expected language pair to support": "VN–EN",
        "Project's current development phase": "Idea",
        "Real-world use case or industry your solution be applied": "Manufacturing",
        "What impact do you expect your solution to create?": "The solution can reduce communication barriers between Vietnamese and English-speaking workers, managers, engineers, and foreign partners in manufacturing environments. It can improve safety, reduce misunderstanding during operations or training, speed up collaboration, and make workplaces more inclusive for multilingual teams. Because it works hands-free and on the edge, it can be useful in real situations where workers cannot constantly hold a phone or depend on a stable internet connection.",
        "How could your solution evolve into a real product or dep...": "The prototype can evolve into a commercial wearable translation product for factories, construction sites, logistics, healthcare support, tourism, and field service teams. Future versions can include custom industry vocabulary, admin dashboards, team deployment management, offline language packs, safety phrase detection, and integration with company training or SOP systems. The product can be offered as a hardware-plus-software solution or as an enterprise SaaS subscription bundled with approved wearable devices.",
