        "Describe your technical approach": "We extract safety intent from speech rather than translating full sentences. A keyword spotter running on the Qualcomm Hexagon DSP detects critical words in Vietnamese or Chinese, then a lightweight slot classifier outputs a minimal structured message, urgency, location, and action, in the target language. Fully on-device, no cloud dependency.",
