        "What impact do you expect your solution to create?": "OneVoice Lens can reduce language barriers in workplaces where misunderstanding can cause delays, safety risks, or poor coordination. It helps workers communicate hands-free, offline, and in real time. The system can improve safety, productivity, and inclusion for multilingual teams, especially in environments where internet connectivity is limited or unreliable.",
