        "Briefly describe your proposed solution": "Empowering users to communicate with each other in the simplest way possible by completely eliminating language barriers.",
        "What makes your solution innovative or different from exi...": "Our solution turns bilingual communication into a truly on‑device, real‑time conversation experience instead of a traditional “sentence‑by‑sentence” translator. It is optimized for natural, low‑latency dialogue on handheld edge devices, working reliably even in low‑connectivity environments without any cloud dependency.\n\nTechnically, we combine streaming ASR → lightweight NMT → neural TTS, all compressed and quantized to run efficiently on edge AI hardware while keeping end‑to‑end latency under 2 seconds. Unlike generic mobile apps, our models are specifically tuned for Vietnamese–English / Vietnamese–Chinese / Vietnamese–Korean conversations and real‑world use cases in factories, logistics, and public services.",
        "Describe your technical approach": "We use a streaming speech‑to‑speech translation pipeline running fully on‑device: on‑device ASR to transcribe the source language, a compact NMT model for bilingual translation, and an efficient neural TTS engine to synthesize the target speech in near real time. All models are pruned, quantized, and deployed via an edge‑optimized runtime to meet the compute and memory limits of handheld devices.\n\nAt system level, audio is processed in small frames so ASR, NMT, and TTS can run in parallel, minimizing perceived latency during conversation. The solution targets handheld edge devices with AI accelerators (e.g., Qualcomm‑based platforms) and is packaged as a standalone application that can operate completely offline while supporting the three focus language pairs of the OneVoice AI Challenge.",
        "Expected language pair to support": "VN–EN, VN–CN, VN–KR",
        "Project's current development phase": "Idea",
        "Real-world use case or industry your solution be applied": "Manufacturing",
        "What impact do you expect your solution to create?": "We expect our solution to make real‑time bilingual communication more accessible, especially in environments with limited or unreliable connectivity such as factories, logistics sites, and construction areas. By running entirely on handheld edge devices, it enables faster, intuitive, and reliable multilingual conversations without depending on the cloud, helping workers, experts, and customers collaborate more safely and productively across Vietnamese–English, Vietnamese–Chinese, and Vietnamese–Korean language barriers.\n\nIn the short term, this can reduce miscommunication in training, operations, and safety procedures for multinational teams, while lowering the cost of deploying translation support in the field. In the longer term, we hope the solution can serve as a practical reference for on‑device AI translation deployments in Vietnam and the wider region, contributing to the challenge’s mission of bringing AI from research into real‑world applications with meaningful social and economic impact.",
        "How could your solution evolve into a real product or dep...": "Over time, our prototype can evolve into a deployable product by packaging the on‑device translation engine into a configurable SDK and reference app that enterprises can integrate into their existing workflows. The first step would be piloting with a few Vietnamese manufacturers, logistics operators, or public‑service units, where handheld edge devices can be issued to frontline staff to support real‑time bilingual communication in training, operations, and safety scenarios.\n\nBased on field‑testing data and user feedback, we can harden the system (performance, UX, security), define pricing and support models, and then scale to broader deployments across factories, ports, and service centers. In parallel, collaboration with Saigon AI Hub, hardware partners, and local integrators would help us adapt the solution to multiple device types and markets, turning it from a competition prototype into a sustainable commercial product used in everyday work.",
