        "Name of your project": "Murmur",
        "Briefly describe your proposed solution": "Our proposed solution is a fully offline, real-time voice translation system that orchestrates Sherpa-ONNX STT, local machine translation (VinAI/EnViT5), and Piper TTS within a Pipecat pipeline to deliver low-latency Vietnamese-to-English speech translation entirely on local edge devices.",
