        "Describe your technical approach": "Our technical approach leverages a modular, offline cascaded pipeline (ASR → MT → TTS) orchestrated by the Pipecat framework to stream and translate speech in real time. We utilize lightweight, quantized AI models—specifically Sherpa-ONNX (Zipformer) for Vietnamese speech-to-text, VinAI/EnViT5 for high-quality local machine translation, and Piper TTS for English speech synthesis. To ensure natural turn-taking and low latency on standard consumer CPUs without requiring a GPU, the system integrates Silero VAD with smart turn analysis, deploying the pipeline locally through a native CustomTkinter desktop UI for local network access.",
