        "How could your solution evolve into a real product or dep...": "The project can evolve into an embedded Vietnamese voice interface for edge devices. The next steps are to collect domain-specific real audio, fine-tune or distill the selected lightweight ASR model, benchmark on target hardware, and integrate streaming audio input. After the ASR module is stable, it can be combined with downstream modules such as command understanding, translation, or TTS depending on the deployment use case.",
